            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While everything is in the oven, boil half a kettle</p><p>Peel and chop the<strong> red onions</strong> roughly and chop the <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> in half</p><p>Top, tail and chop the <strong>courgette<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</strong> </span>into bite-sized pieces</p><p>Dissolve the <strong>vegetable stock mix</strong> in 50ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> [100ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>While the chicken is cooking, heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>olive oil</strong> over a medium heat</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-5-1642089888079-x200.jpg",
