            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once hot, add the<strong> chopped</strong> <strong>red</strong> <strong>onion</strong>, <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>courgette </strong>and<strong> tomato paste</strong> to the pan and cook for 2-3 min or until starting to soften</p><p>Add the <strong>halved cherry tomatoes</strong> and cook for 4-5 min further or until all the veg has fully softened</p><p>Add the <strong>vegetable stock</strong> and cook for 1-2 min further</p><p>Season generously with <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> – this is your <strong>Mediterranean veg</strong></p>",
